en he skidded off the road.\", \"from\": 7500, \"to\": 7631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evenepoel\", \"from\": 7511, \"to\": 7520}, {\"ngram\": \"a broken collarbone\", \"from\": 7530, \"to\": 7549}, {\"ngram\": \"fractures\", \"from\": 7564, \"to\": 7573}, {\"ngram\": \"his clavicle\", \"from\": 7577, \"to\": 7589}, {\"ngram\": \"scapula\", \"from\": 7594, \"to\": 7601}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 7622, \"to\": 7630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Soudal Quick-Step rider also managed to make it back for the pre-Tour warm-up race but was off the pace when the race went uphill.\", \"from\": 7632, \"to\": 7766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Soudal Quick-Step rider\", \"from\": 7632, \"to\": 7659}, {\"ngram\": \"the pre-Tour warm-up race\", \"from\": 7693, \"to\": 7718}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 7731, \"to\": 7739}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 7745, \"to\": 7753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was Vingegaard who was the worst affected by the crash,suffering a collapsed lung alongside broken ribs and collarbone.\", \"from\": 7768, \"to\": 7899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vingegaard\", \"from\": 7784, \"to\": 7794}, {\"ngram\": \"the crash\", \"from\": 7825, \"to\": 7834}, {\"ngram\": \"a collapsed lung\", \"from\": 7845, \"to\": 7861}, {\"ngram\": \"broken ribs\", \"from\": 7872, \"to\": 7883}, {\"ngram\": \"collarbone\", \"from\": 7888, \"to\": 7898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dane would not return to action until the Grand D\\u00e8part for the Tour de France at the end of June, almost three months after the incident.\", \"from\": 7900, \"to\": 8041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7967, \"end\": 7981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.224955562168122e-56, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phra