\"Adevastating crash\", \"from\": 12868, \"to\": 12886}, {\"ngram\": \"the exit\", \"from\": 12890, \"to\": 12898}, {\"ngram\": \"a roundaboutsaw Vollering crash\", \"from\": 12902, \"to\": 12933}, {\"ngram\": \"6.3km\", \"from\": 12944, \"to\": 12949}, {\"ngram\": \"stage\", \"from\": 12959, \"to\": 12964}, {\"ngram\": \"her bike\", \"from\": 13013, \"to\": 13021}, {\"ngram\": \"49 seconds\", \"from\": 13026, \"to\": 13036}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 13056, \"to\": 13064}, {\"ngram\": \"her left leg\", \"from\": 13068, \"to\": 13080}, {\"ngram\": \"a hip injury\", \"from\": 13106, \"to\": 13118}, {\"ngram\": \"her bike\", \"from\": 13143, \"to\": 13151}, {\"ngram\": \"her way\", \"from\": 13160, \"to\": 13167}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 13171, \"to\": 13181}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 13211, \"to\": 13218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The overall classification completely flipped on its head when Vollering crossed the line 1:47 behind her teammate and stage winner Blanka Vas, but more importantly, she had also lost 1:19 to Kasia Niewiadoma (Canyon-SRAM) heading into the final three stages.\", \"from\": 13242, \"to\": 13501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13374, \"end\": 13384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\", \"score\": 0.9999999946303433, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blanka Vas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blanka_Vas\"}, {\"begin\": 13434, \"end\": 13450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kasia Niewiadoma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarzyna_Niewiadoma\"}, {\"begin\": 13452, \"end\": 13463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"score\": 0.9294047605330832, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canyon-SRAM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canyon\\u2013SRAM\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The overall classification\", \"from\": 13242, \"to\": 13268}, {\"ngram\": \"its head\", \"from\": 13291, \"to\": 13299}, {\"ngram\": \"Vollering\", \"from\": 13305, \"to\": 13314}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 13323, \"to\": 13331}, {\"ngram\": \"the final three stages\", \"from\": 13478, \"to\": 13500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Questions swirled around the SD Worx-Protime's tactics and why their yellow jersey was left isolated in the closing kilometres of this stage, but her teammates and the riders from rival teams who had split off the front said they did not realize Vollering was involved in the crash, but that there was little that could be done with such a short distance to the finish line.\", \"from\": 13503, \"to\": 13877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13572, \"end\": 13585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0029750650426203e-143, \"text\": \"yellow jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Questions\", \"from\": 13503, \"to\": 13512}, {\"ngram\": \"the SD Worx-Protime's tactics\", \"from\": 13528, \"to\": 13557}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing kilometres\", \"from\": 13607, \"to\": 13629}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 13633, \"to\": 13643}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 13649, \"to\": 13662}, {\"ngram\": \"the riders\", \"from\": 13667, \"to\": 13677}, {\"ngram\": \"rival teams\", \"from\": 13683, \"to\": 13694}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 13713, \"to\": 13722}, {\"ngram\": \"Vollering\", \"from\": 13749, \"to\": 13758}, {\"ngram\": \"the crash\", \"from