\", \"from\": 19721, \"to\": 19730}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall champion\", \"from\": 19737, \"to\": 19757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She pulled on the maglia rosa after the stage 1 time trial in Brescia, and then carryied the race lead through Volta Mantovana, Toano, Urbino, Foligno, Chieti and to the top of the iconic Blockhaus, in what was a dramatic race for time bonuses on the penultimate queen stage 7 against runner-up Lotte Kopecky (SD Worx-Protime).\", \"from\": 19760, \"to\": 20087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19822, \"end\": 19829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brescia\", \"score\": 0.9320170552473797, \"rank\": 0.0729417389623709, \"text\": \"Brescia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brescia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brescia\"}, {\"begin\": 19871, \"end\": 19886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volta_Mantovana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Volta Mantovana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volta_Mantovana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volta_Mantovana\"}, {\"begin\": 19888, \"end\": 19893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toano,_Virginia\", \"score\": 0.9087328061873676, \"rank\": 0.05889423076929021, \"text\": \"Toano\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toano,_Virginia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toano,_Virginia\"}, {\"begin\": 19895, \"end\": 19901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Urbino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.314989676732676e-21, \"text\": \"Urbino\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Urbino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Urbino\"}, {\"begin\": 19903, \"end\": 19910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foligno\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3154077764956495e-21, \"text\": \"Foligno\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foligno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://